</ul>

<h3>B-sides, Reissues &amp; Deep Cuts</h3>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Street_Spirit_(Fade_Out)">Talk Show Host</a> - b-side, Street Spirit single; used in Romeo + Juliet</li>
  <li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Daily_Mail_(song)">The Daily Mail / Staircase</a> - standalone 2011; both better than half of TKOL</li>
  <li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spectre_(song)">Spectre</a> - written for Bond, rejected, released Christmas 2015</li>
  <li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/I_Might_Be_Wrong:_Live_Recordings">I Might Be Wrong: Live Recordings</a> - mini live album, Kid A/Amnesiac tours; essential</li>
